These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, train, taxi
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up, tea
1. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
3. the person drinking sprite is the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking 7up is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Transport   | taxi | skateboard | train |
| Beverage    | 7up    | tea | sprite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
City: rome, new-york, marseilles
There 3 different types of food: zucchini, raspberry, strawberry
1. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
2. the person eating raspberry is in an even position##4
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person eating raspberry is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| City       | new-york | marseilles | rome |
| Food   | strawberry    | raspberry     | zucchini        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
House: futuristic, farmhouse, cottage
City: marseilles, colone, san-francisco
1. the futuristic house is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the farmhouse house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| House         | cottage     | farmhouse | futuristic |
| City   | colone | marseilles     | san-francisco  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, bolivar, dannemann
3 different games are played: chess, poker, go
1. the bolivar-smoker is the person playing poker##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is the person playing go##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Cigar   | dannemann | bolivar  | old-henry  |
| Game         | chess  | poker | go |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, game, prince
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, motorbike, car
1. the prince-smoker is between the dunhill-smoker and the person driving the skateboard##2
2. the game-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Cigar         | dunhill   | prince | game    |
| Transport   | motorbike | car     | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, thai, pakistani
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, mystery
1. the turkish is the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is the thai##1
3. the thai is in an odd position##4
4. the pakistani is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | thai | pakistani | turkish   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery     | animation    | comedy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, juice
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, may, march
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking sprite is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person drinking juice##2
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Beverage   | juice | sprite | tea |
| Birthday           | may         | january         | march |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, ivory, red
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, dahlia, begonia
1. the person who growszinnia is between the person who growsdahlia and the person who likes apricot##2
2. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Color   | ivory | red | apricot |
| Flower    | dahlia    | zinnia | begonia     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, pink, light-blue
City: marseilles, edinburgh, nizza
1. the person traveling to nizza is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Color   | light-blue   | pink  | blue  |
| City         | nizza | edinburgh | marseilles |

