.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
3 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, chess
3 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, ferret
1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Game   | snooker    | chess      | scrabble |
| Pet       | hamster | ferret | frog   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
3 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, whist
City: london, paris, new-york
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person traveling to london is the person playing canasta##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is the person playing whist##1
4. the person playing whist is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Game         | mah-jongg | whist | canasta |
| City   | paris | new-york   | london |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, fantasy, disaster
There 3 different types of food: spinach, cucumber, apple
1. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
2. the person watching spy movies is the person eating apple##1
3. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
4. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | fantasy | spy |
| Food     | cucumber     | spinach   | apple        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, march, april
City: hannover, rome, london
1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Birthday   | april  | december | march   |
| City         | rome | london   | hannover |

