.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, february, december
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, punk, gospel
1. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in february and the fan of punk##2
2. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of punk is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Birthday   | february | december | april |
| Music-Genre     | indie    | gospel  | punk   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
