2. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
4. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | milk     | iced-tea |
| Pet   | hamster | fish | turtle    |

