3 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, mah-jongg
1. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Color   | purple | brown | fuchsia    |
| Game           | monopoly     | mah-jongg  | backgammon |

