.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
House: townhouse, futuristic, wooden
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, fonseca, ritmeester
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the townhouse house##1
2. the townhouse house is in the middle##1
3. the wooden house is the fonseca-smoker##1
4. the baccarat-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| House         | wooden | townhouse   | futuristic |
| Cigar   | fonseca   | baccarat | ritmeester      |

