.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, pineapple, plum
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, drawing, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
2. the person eating cucumber is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Food      | cucumber | pineapple | plum |
| Hobby   | drawing   | magic-tricks          | card-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, whist
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, cabbage, lime
1. the person eating lime is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating lime is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
4. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Game     | backgammon  | whist   | mah-jongg |
| Food   | lime | cabbage | watermelon       |

 